data.description: Looking for privacy and seclusion but still convenient to shopping, restaurants and highway?  Here it is! 8 wooded acres in a growing and exciting part of Cherokee Co! This adorable two bedroom home has been updated inside and out!! New flooring, New exterior and interior paint, updated kitchen with butcher block countertops, and bright and airy colors throughout home. New front deck built. The full bath has been completely renovated with beautiful vanity and backsplash. There is also a secondary home site to build a dream home on! So much potential ready to go on this great property!!
